Interface Summary

F<A,B> A transformation or function from A to B.

F4<A,B,C,D,E> A transformation function of arity-4 from A, B, C and D to E.
F5<A,B,C,D,E,F$> A transformation function of arity-5 from A, B, C, D and E to F$.
F6<A,B,C,D,E,F$,G> A transformation function of arity-6 from A, B, C, D, E and F$ to G.
F7<A,B,C,D,E,F$,G,H> A transformation function of arity-7 from A, B, C, D, E, F$ and G to H.
F8<A,B,C,D,E,F$,G,H,I> A transformation function of arity-8 from A, B, C, D, E, F$, G and H to I.
